fields.name: PrimingJobDetails
fields.description: The job details or error information if any.

fields.name: PrimingJobId
fields.description: The unique identifier of the priming job.

fields.name: PrimingJobPercentComplete
fields.description: The current progress of the priming job, as a percentage.

fields.name: PrimingJobState
fields.description: The state of the priming operation.

fields.name: PrimingJobStatus
fields.description: The status code of the priming job.

fields.name: PrimingManifestUrl
fields.description: The URL for the priming manifest file to download. This file must be readable from the HPC Cache. When the file is in Azure blob storage the URL should include a Shared Access Signature (SAS) granting read permissions on the blob.
